---
import Col from '../../ui/Col.astro'
import Row from '../../ui/Row.astro'
import Section from '../../ui/Section.astro'
---

<Section id="about-hero" mode="light">
	<Row>
		<Col span="8" classes="flex flex-col justify-center z-10 relative">
			<p class="mb-6 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-500">
				DECISION-GRADE GRID INTELLIGENCE
			</p>
			<h1 class="mb-8 font-headings text-3xl font-bold leading-tight lg:text-4xl">
				Strategic insight into Germany’s evolving grid landscape.
			</h1>
			<p class="max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
				Revolt combines project-specific grid intelligence with strategic advisory to support energy
				infrastructure development across Germany’s increasingly constrained electricity networks.
			</p>
		</Col>
	</Row>
</Section>
